Put a favicon.ico or favicon.svg (preferred) in your public/ folder and add favicon_link_tag "favicon.svg" to your layout inside the <head></head> tags.

You may optionally reach for the meta_tags gem and do this all dynamically. This is on the roadmap to support in the future.

Below are the recommended tags to include for best discoverability between apps and services.

Generate icons:
https://www.favicon-generator.org/

Tips: Before generating all icons, I typically start with a icon that is atleast 512x512 in size. It can have a transparent background (.png, .svg) but I'd recommend something more bold and easily discoverable.

